Set this item to only Forged and Sharpshooter because the other classes do not have an equivalent shoulders.

column5: NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "A00E473C413581BCF580DD83D25BF22E", "\"Earth trembles below. Dust stings my eyes, from above. The work, it endures.\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "F6B8374943BBCF5F2D8413B5B12F7C9B", "\"... the more Omensius tapped into his deep reserves of mana, the more efficient he became at harnessing the power of Ember.\"\r\nThe Book of Dusk: Chapter 1, pg. 8")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "132F3F4649607BBF9F5075AB5E72AA4C", "\"For every foot of track, walk a mile in your boots. Feel the pulse of the ground, while your Railhammer pounds.\" - Old Hammer Song")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "404B31BE4404D572B7E7C9B19538111A", "\"Your weapon is only as good as your aim.\" - Sharpshooter Proverb")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "589F23FE49526B3216A5C59396611726", "During the height of the dwarven empires, their subjugation of goblins was so complete that it led to a golden age for the nearby varkenin tribes.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "B788025B46C987ABD3B2E6AED195F9C4", "The nimble legs of the Hyvid worker and drone castes allow them to move swiftly along hive-encrusted rock walls, creeping out of any crevice. Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "34D147C742CA222DCE763CB3ACA3E4E6", "\"My heart pounds slowly. The mountain, she answers it. The sound of progress.\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "3B04F42447861C309AB4D79D69C1A342", "\"Estarielle, First Star of Dusk, brilliant daughter, just as the disk of the Sun fades behind the mountains, so shines brighter the light of the moon. Know that even on the darkest night, there is always light for you.\"\r\nThe Book of Dusk: Chapter 6, pg. 18")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "7521F9A9480080B542C97DBDEFC8227A", "\"To invert dents in the chest cover, apply blunt reverse pressure from within. If you cannot access the dented area with the chest in place, it may have to be detached from the endoskeleton.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Workshop Manual")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "990EEC6D4B2B40133C758DA352ACDA54", "\"Daddy put a hammer in my hand the day I was born. Been swingin\' that hammer every eve and every morn.\" - Old Hammer Song")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "227C95494505E7DD9C732984C85C4BD9", "\"Take what you need and then take a little more for the times you can take nothing.\"\r\n- Sharpshooter Proverb")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "6455174C401A0D37087996B1A62316B2", "Few have driven deep enough east into the goblin homeland to see what lies on its rocky far shores.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "B10C918347F013D6D7BDFA84B2C881F0", "\"The rate at which the Hyvid evolve is startling. Guardians not only protect the egg pods, they also appear to determine the form and caste the Hyvid will take, to meet the hive\'s needs.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "4B1444CB4630CD3750D3C5A7D4ED9DBD", "\"Gloved hands grip rough stone. The rock yields its prize: a gem. More ember for the forge.\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "496A4C7B405397325CF0BCBD458447D8", "\"You, Estarielle, shall be the First Star of Dusk, for your light glows strong. Cast your light upon others that they may bask in its warmth or cower in fear.\"\r\n- The Book of Dusk: Chapter 6, pg. 17")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "DDD97A6744FDEDAD419CD895A61B879B", "\"It is recommended that you replace the actuator rods in your FRG-0 every ten years or 30,000 compressions, whichever comes first.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Manual")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "F520D1D4408D645DBE9515BF21933C30", "\"Grip the hammer tight with your calloused hands. Gloves cover you nice when the flame wave lands.\" - Old Hammer Song")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "7637A0C34FCAAAE9DAC3E39AAD39CF15", "\"The greatest gift a sharpshooter can give is to place their spirit into a trinket for future generations to use.\"\r\n- Sharpshooter Proverb")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "0B0D09134CDAC616B651B7A6AE7388BD", "Even soldiers quake at the campfire stories of the varkenin, the forest beast-men who live deep among the trees.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "33D02789471A3FED8CC4D594F0B83AC0", "\"The hooked forelegs of the Hyvid soldier caste have clearly been adapted and possibly sharpened to be used in combat.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "68DF655A48A969E83EB265B4A5B3A5AA", "\"Earth trembles below. Dust stings my eyes, from above. The work, it endures.\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "E7BE3C9A41A8F46982190BB23B9DD214", "\"Warning: only lubricants rated class D or higher are approved for use on model FRG-0 hatches, due to extreme heat and pressure levels.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Manual")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "227BF6F24B634A200F26C49059FED6F3", "During the height of the dwarven empires, their subjugation of goblins was so complete that it led to a golden age for the nearby varkenin tribes.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "561E1F564E2596990FD9B6914669E5FB", "\"The nimble legs of the Hyvid worker and drone castes allow them to move swiftly along hive-encrusted rock walls, creeping out of any crevice.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "930C3DD54040BB614956F6B1B87A0D25", "\"Plans swiftly take form. Gears clanking and whirring. The army, it grows.\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "2EF4E9A34BAEACDEB15822873EA695C9", "\"Closing her unseeing eyes, Estarielle reached out to the inky depths of the pre-dawn darkness. Feeling it enter her mind, erasing her fears, she became one with it and whispered one word: \'Begone.\'\"\r\n- The Book of Dusk: Chapter 9, pg 40")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "E073B59B4437780F314D50BBC460F453", "\"Note: some reports indicate that not all helm collar or cowlings may be fully fit compatible with every FRG-0 head model. If you are having difficulty attaching a collar or cowling, please adjust the neck rod to compensate.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Manual")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "4AB8E58D4231FDE0AA8DE1A5040494EA", "\"I know a thing or two about drivin\' that train. Roll on over to you, gonna bring ya that pain.\" - Old Hammer Song")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "D17F201D4CCB3833C1720D9D802E81FE", "\"Anything can be ammo if you see it as such.\"\r\n- Sharpshooter Proverb")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "3699EC5245B06E011337C8B968840182", "The mournful howls heard deep within the goblin forest do not always come from goblins...")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "FEED07ED4012FEC6181B71B467F44187", "\"The Hyvid\'s antennae must be used for communication among hive members, but they also seem strangely agitated around ember crystals. Could it be agitating them?\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "C38BD72B4B00F8AB356BB6BE8B7B5BA6", "\"The machines hunger. Ember. Oil. Steam. Iron. Who is in charge?\" - Elegy of the Mountain")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "244345894856BDD7684E79833BCA626C", "\"The machines hunger. Ember. Oil. Steam. Iron. Who is in charge?\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "418FA40844DF1A76E7FAD19D3A81DAD2", "\"Beware that you do not overtighten the locomotion retaining ring when replacing the locomotion form on your FRG-0, or the attachment grooves may become stripped bare.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Manual")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "3577DB00419988BFF29BC7A60FC988D6", "\"Beware that you do not overtighten the locomotion retaining ring when replacing the locomotion form on your FRG-0, or the attachment grooves may become stripped bare.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Manual")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "9D6B767A451A7816892A4BAE5F6011F3", "Varkenin have a nurturing respect for the land, living between trees rather than felling them. Even the goblin skins they use for their tents are all natural.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "97C080D34FDFEE9F807C3C9C1B4D5F0C", "\"The bioluminescent hindquarters of the Hyvid Guardians contain a strange acidic compound that serves as some form of evolutionary catalyst.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "40B25DF548A166704BBF2984F62E3037", "\"The bioluminescent hindquarters of the Hyvid Guardians contain a strange acidic compound that serves as some form of evolutionary catalyst.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "64C881624B334400A043C18B02E97608", "\"The machines hunger. Ember. Oil. Steam. Iron. Who is in charge?\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "3C22668E46DD414F8702FCA50158C70A", "\"Omensius sought out the relics hidden in the dark corners of the world, knowing that he could use their gifts for good, unlike others.\"\r\n- The Book of Dusk: Chapter 6, pg. 23")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "A774C0BB48A58AC02DFF829135E68EA8", "\"I\'ve got somethin\' special in my pocket. It keeps me fresh like a rocket.\" - Old Hammer Song")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "6FC63D3040D9A2DD12D78E895D7DCC7B", "\"Some will call you a scoundrel for your efforts to collect artifacts, but a well-placed arrow silences wagging tongues.\"\r\n- Sharpshooter Proverb")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "2A58E0D64B54432B183C71B2F9100A39", "Varkenin have a nurturing respect for the land, living between trees rather than felling them. Even the goblin skins they use for their tents are all natural.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "C536E6DE4C329433B66A67AEDE593F8A", "\"The bioluminescent hindquarters of the Hyvid Guardians contain a strange acidic compound that serves as some form of evolutionary catalyst.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "FF38ADE54E6955FC561015A14050427E", "\"Shoulders ache from work. The cost of building the hall. Dwarven might is strong.\" - Elegy of the Mountain")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "481089C24E329BA339FEAA88ED73D5F2", "\"The risks weighed heavily upon Omensius\' shoulders as he tapped into the very aetherial forces scratching at the edges of the world. But he knew that throwing the netherim at his foes would eventually result in their demise.\"\r\n- The Book of Dusk: Chapter 8, pg 32")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "50343B1D4D1C71623DB98FB6DD7EA5D6", "\"While unnecessary for standard uses, optional protective panels may be attached to the shoulder attachment points of the endoskeleton.\" - Haenz Forged FRG-0 Owner\'s Workshop Manual")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "B1D0780945C3BE54A93016AC42D632A2", "\"O\'er my shoulder, is that daddy\'s hammer? Swingin\' so hard, goin\' a-wham-jama-slamma.\" - Old Hammer Song")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "E028F6254B82C099B8F82D947E0AAFA3", "\"Only a fool lets a foe stand closer than a bow\'s length.\"\r\n- Sharpshooter Proverb")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "5AA6F17148B9DCB4B30076A6945A6A12", "The scars of skirmishes between goblins and varkenin tell the tale of the constant conflict between these neighboring creatures.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "AA8618AF40706B03920EF1AF37D6573D", "\"Hyvid eggs lay dormant in their creches for long stretches of time, but as young Arcli learned, the sound of your footfalls triggers their swift, ravenous hatching.\" - Prof. Stoker\'s Bug Book")

column5: NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "151E760C44062657E609F89E959998C8", "The finest bow crafted by the legendary bowyer Herman, shortly before he mysteriously vanished.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "3E120C5D40B9CC82AC8E0C9A237F49B7", "Who says you can\'t capture a storm and use magic to infuse it into a bow?")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "1781CC0044DB2408163A6D97FE64A84D", "Forged from the remains of dragon whose name has been lost to history, this bow fires arrows with unparalled force.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "6C1F1FD041A771AE5F0E2FBF663AD4E5", "Inspectors from the Automatonics Guild were known to accept bribes to overlook firing rate limiters, despite the inherent risk of unit failure.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "F27C26A2432C8DF6332A2BBC4AD522E6", "Skelve Gruntvir was purused across the dwarven kingdoms after it was revealed that his automatons murdered his rivals with unlicensed poison darts.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "1A10AC8E4E8C2543DF80DA9663D57EED", "Mega Blaster! For the Forged for whom subtlety is not their strong suit.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "2E040EC643FE0947CD441AB8C33A6796", "Mr. Toasty has fire for you! Burn, meat!")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "BCF131924465AF6461C6A397FE083737", "\"Venting: maintain 10m clearance around the Forged when steam levels approach 90%. While typically heat is vented in a single blast, overclocked systems can result in multiple, staggered releases...\"  - Dwarven Forged Manual")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "F2E7559A448FE05D70F9328252AB8E13", "With the end of every night comes the dawn of a new day, for as long as that lasts.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "BBDE842B44C45DC8185905826D0A0AFB", "Uncontrolled chaos can be intoxicating. Be certain you have a firm hold on reality before use.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "9A94642441F4FC626CE3C4A4CBB83D40", "...as the black sun rose, violent flames eagerly sought out the unrepentent wicked.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Digitus_Panoptifist_FlavorText", "They\'re always watching. Always ready to jump in.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "817933B84331ADC35D53FA9A9D8E4498", "It\'s not vampirism per se, it\'s more like a vitality exchange.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Focus_BirdsEyeFocus_FlavorText", "I see you there, and I strike like lightning.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "9C6D8B2242468E338008D4B19989E925", "The charge of the Dawnbearer is to lead the way out of darkness, to a new day, another chance.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "7448D3AB43A6814E8EF040A79B94E777", "You can always make time, when you\'ve got magic on your side.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "FDF62E8341FA31A82D8916AE0106949D", "\"Do you think we can handle \'em?\" asked the panicked Embermage. The Railmaster simply smiled and lit his doompipe in reply.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Focus_EggOfWonder_FlavorText", "They say the faces of certain cards in the Deck of Wonders were painted with pigments derived from the blood of unhatched Hyvid eggs.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Focus_HeadOfBlastbutt_FlavorText", "Chief Blastbutt was always first into every fight, but he had trouble getting troops to stand behind him.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "4FAFBF834D612FE85798BB845491B3F9", "King Snaggletooth eventually grew so corpulent and torpid that he became truly one with his throne, attended by his ratlin subjects.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "AAA8B1F545E31C5449A61A821024AE93", "Some soldiers are so dedicated to General Graye that not even death can end their service.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "1D561392453F86C811F8328CAF762DE9", "Of course it doesn\'t contain actual souls... right?")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Focus_TomeOfZulTova_FlavorText", "Hidden among his ledgers of wealth unimaginable lie one of the secrets to Zul-Tova\'s riches: The Tome of Zul-Tova, a cursed book offering gold in exchange for madness.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "A58D5D7A4A6CEDCCCBC3258610874D51", "Literally pure destruction.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "07B1AD7A4736447FB4DD17BF78A59674", "Bring out yer dead.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "F37678014C69024EE5644790A8FB859F", "Take the Beater, my son. Go forth. Let none stand in your way.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_GreatWeapon_SwordOfTheLost_FlavorText", "My friends would never leave me.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "D1B7A52242ADB6B04F64939A48CF2AFF", "I do two things well: I break things and I blast things.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "B59CBBCC4E1E891582CCA8ADCD0D03E0", "Stolen from the Varkenin shaman Goldfur, Wideload made quite a mess of the paleskin caverns with this enchanted mace...")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "DF97F0C84A21636DDE5D04BEAF56279F", "\"What do we fear? Nothing! What do we break? Faces!\" - Old Valgang War Chant")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "7E5EB0C94A3E0E716496A3A35406109B", "Don\'t get fleeced: park a monster in front of this mace and jack it up.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "D77F8716435A0BE84AC446A83580AB8A", "Honey? Have you seen my mace brush? There\'s gore all over this one.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "FE7829F141D309FC0F081EA15A3E9359", "This goose roasts you.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "647F4F714CC857290160009D18D80383", "One of the most agonizing poisons is known as Dead Man\'s Bones, because it is a vile contagious that persists even deep within discarded bones.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Pistol_Zapshot_FlavorText", "Mind the zap.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "B37BCD7D4076B1259C896C8405B516EE", "It\'s a common misconception that the Railmaster\'s train is fully steam-powered.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "CF394C4642E659820245DD9A38EC207F", "The Railmasters don\'t often speak of the few in their ranks who take their enjoyment of using the hammer too far. For those bloodthirsty Railmasters, efficiency in crushing monsters becomes more important than laying rails.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "A63FF6AC425DE5E0CB414BA22686FA1B", "Constructed with a graphite and astarite blend shaft and highly reactive counterweights in the head, the Centrifugal Demolisher is ideal for any construction site, besieged keep or goblin-infested cave.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "A5C116F0474D9294578F84BB323A75F7", "A low, mournful chant rumbled beneath the pounding sound of the Deadhammer.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "BC70BA8F46ACEB9D43234BB0A1097CD5", "Don\'t go swimming in a storm, don\'t stand next to trees under thunderclouds and don\'t get shot by Heart Shocker.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "A81D692A42F5186E57CDA7867267C717", "If u haf da ryeful, u da leedah.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "38B9A22348BD100F82605292FCB7388D", "Dragons don\'t hit often, and they never have to hit more than once.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Rifle_Viperstriker_FlavorText", "Harvesting skyviper venom is a trickier business than you might even guess.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Shield_Boneblocker_FlavorText", "The wall of bones knows nothing of death.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "9979FBAF4DB40C5F4ECC55AC55338A14", "Kalacama scavvers were notorious for stripping traps from ancient ruins, wielding them as weapons on ruin runs.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Shield_Firewall_FlavorText", "Just go ahead and hit me.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Shield_Frostwall_FlavorText", "Those Valgang tribes that settled furthest to the north were known to be masters of Frostreaving: using the very ice around them for protection.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "9D13D1CD443EDEAD7D4F929EB665443B", "His Wooly Hooliness sends his regards...")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "D1339EE04DCBDE14502679B06D932B3A", "The spirits of Railmasters past echo down through the ages, ready to be called upon by the truest of Railmasters.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "D141B2FB4455045E39FCA5A0E3A173AD", "Gripped by darkness, struck by lightning.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "AE618E6E493B2818BAE375B0E487C4FE", "Shasta protects those she loves. Now and forever.")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "0E15F76545E272453C16B69015592152", "Shotgonne Squad Six was an elite group of raiders dispatched into enemy encampments. Their custom shields are still highly prized for shotgonne aficionados.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "DB6478E347C868F47A8C05B0CCA1D3A2", "Valgang warriors brew a tea from Bitterwood root to build up poison immunity.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Staff_ClockworkStaff_FlavorText", "I just need a little more time. Luckily, I can make some time.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "C17404974FAB0B62EBD52F9FD23703CC", "It\'s a bad idea to go into any infestation without some form of protection.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Staff_SneckoStick_FlavorText", "It\'s not perplexing, just very, very painful.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Sword_BloodDrinker_FlavorText", "Surely there\'s enough blood to go around.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Sword_BoneRazor_FlavorText", "Cuts to the bone.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Sword_Deadblade_FlavorText", "It\'s a dead man\'s party and this party doesn\'t stop.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "07CBE554487B381B38DD919B4A1698DC", "\"Back off! Just back off!\" - The Firestarter")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "FFE8345E481F893D50B4B58C24B8EF1D", "Besides the grounding boots and gloves the Railmasters wear, they also undergo arduous training to build up their electrical resistance.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Sword_MagmaSlam_FlavorText", "Burn and Destroy!")

NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "276E9BAA42D63244B5888195847C12C9", "Following a six month reign atop the Death Tower, replicas of Grindor IV\'s Servo-Blade sold for small fortunes, as Dwarven lords sought to build their next champion.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "417022A34B0D3DAA2EF7F78FE88E2482", "Hyvid parts are useful for many things, if you manage not to poison, burn, or cut yourself while handling them.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "Weapon_Legendary_Sword_UnboundBlade_FlavorText", "The Maestro\'s strikes were so fast that it seemed like his blade came unbound from its hilt.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "DC2BB50C4BC76C0EAAF9BC9D3516EA85", "Use this item to obtain this decoration for your fort.")

column3: NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "8759713D4800FA538EA52393FB376CC6", "Consume this to gain a bonus amount of Wood Logs.")
NSLOCTEXT("ItemsTable", "829C3C0A453306F732211692A85CCAE9", "Consume this to gain a bonus amount of Wood Planks.")
